episodes.title: Inside the Documentary Series Escaping Twin Flames | Netflix
episodes.description:
Filmmaking team Cecilia Peck and Inbal Lessner discuss their working style, and how Escaping Twin Flames came to be with moderator Tyler Coates, at the Netflix FYSEE space in Los Angeles.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81615920

About Netflix:

A couple built a spiritual business to help people find true love. Now, former followers are sharing their disturbing practices in this docuseries.
